svg.title: {\displaystyle {\begin{aligned}0&=g(\eta ){\frac {d}{d\eta }}\int _{x}h(x)e^{\eta T(x)}\,dx+g'(\eta )\int _{x}h(x)e^{\eta T(x)}\,dx\\&=g(\eta )\int _{x}h(x)\left({\frac {d}{d\eta }}e^{\eta T(x)}\right)\,dx+g'(\eta )\int _{x}h(x)e^{\eta T(x)}\,dx\\&=g(\eta )\int _{x}h(x)e^{\eta T(x)}T(x)\,dx+g'(\eta )\int _{x}h(x)e^{\eta T(x)}\,dx\\&=\int _{x}T(x)g(\eta )h(x)e^{\eta T(x)}\,dx+{\frac {g'(\eta )}{g(\eta )}}\int _{x}g(\eta )h(x)e^{\eta T(x)}\,dx\\&=\int _{x}T(x)p(x)\,dx+{\frac {g'(\eta )}{g(\eta )}}\int _{x}p(x)\,dx\\&=\operatorname {E} [T(x)]+{\frac {g'(\eta )}{g(\eta )}}\\&=\operatorname {E} [T(x)]+{\frac {d}{d\eta }}\ln g(\eta )\end{aligned}}}
